                                                                              \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#you-use-lightroom-cc-instead-of-classic\"\u003eYou Use Lightroom CC Instead of Classic\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#you-do-most-of-your-editing-in-photoshop\"\u003eYou Do Most of Your Editing in Photoshop\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#you-forgot-to-make-an-edit-in-lightroom\"\u003eYou Forgot to Make an Edit in Lightroom\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n            \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDespite being used by many photographers, you probably don\u0026#39;t need to use Camera Raw. In many cases, doing so will add little benefit and simultaneously increase your editing time. However, there are a couple of instances where Camera Raw makes sense.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"you-use-lightroom-cc-instead-of-classic\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            You Use Lightroom CC Instead of Classic\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThough Lightroom CC now has the color calibration tool (and I have indeed \u003ca href=\"http://www.makeuseof.com/lightroom-cc-vs-classic-calibration/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eswitched immediately from Lightroom Classic\u003c/a\u003e as I promised), it still misses a few features that you\u0026#39;ll find in Camera Raw. For example, you can\u0026#39;t move the histogram by clicking on it.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe histogram tool is ideal for keeping your image\u0026#39;s light levels consistent. It\u0026#39;s useful even if you just look at it, but actually managing each section is even better.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2880\" height=\"1510\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Using the Camera Raw App to Edit a Photo From Photoshop\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-13-at-10-53-01.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCamera Raw is also better if you want to edit your picture with a grid format applied. Doing so will help you get more finetuned adjustments.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"you-do-most-of-your-editing-in-photoshop\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e2 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            You Do Most of Your Editing in Photoshop\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSome users prefer editing in Photoshop because of the interface, while others prefer its features and can organize their workflows better. You can also \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/3d-pop-out-photo-effect-photoshop/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emake pop-out photo effects\u003c/a\u003e and more from within the app. If you\u0026#39;re one of these people, using Camera Raw makes more sense.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2880\" height=\"1568\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Using a Graph in the Camera Raw app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-24-at-16-32-30.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRather than having to import your images, you can keep everything in one place and complete your edits more effectively. This is particularly true when Camera Raw has many of the same editing sliders as Lightroom.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"you-forgot-to-make-an-edit-in-lightroom\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            You Forgot to Make an Edit in Lightroom\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven if you have a well-defined Lightroom editing workflow that you\u0026#39;ve done hundreds of times, you\u0026#39;ll still sometimes forget to make adjustments. You might also look at your image after editing it and realize that you don\u0026#39;t like how it looks.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIn both cases, Camera Raw is good for making small adjustments. After applying these, you can then continue with your edits as normal.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2874\" height=\"1516\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Automatically straightening an image in a photo editing app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/auto-straightener-photo-editing.jpeg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEveryone says RAW is the way to go, but is it really? While it offers more editing power, sometimes it\u0026#39;s just overkill. If you\u0026#39;re editing with Camera Raw just because \u0026#34;it\u0026#39;s better,\u0026#34; you might be wasting time.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
